build:
  number: 7
  # x64 OSX is actually overriding the assets from PyPI.org wheel
  skip: True  # [osx and x86_64]

requirements:
  build:
    - python                                 # [build_platform != target_platform]
    - cross-python_{{ target_platform }}     # [build_platform != target_platform]
    - cython                                 # [build_platform != target_platform]
    - {{ compiler('c') }}
    - {{ compiler('cxx') }}
    - cmake
    - make   # [not win]
    - ninja  # [win]
  host:
    - python
    - cython
    - setuptools
  run:
    - python
    - numpy
    - matplotlib-base

test:
  imports:
    - CoolProp
    - CoolProp.tests
    - CoolProp.Plots  # [not py2k or not linux]
    - CoolProp.GUI

about:
  home: https://github.com/CoolProp/CoolProp
  license: MIT
  license_family: MIT
  license_file: LICENSE
  summary: Open-source thermodynamic and transport properties database

  description: |
    Open-source thermodynamic and transport properties database
  doc_url: http://www.coolprop.org/
  dev_url: https://github.com/CoolProp/CoolProp

extra:
  recipe-maintainers:
    - danilomendesdias
    - fcollonval
